snippet.textDisplay:
Two Gills Representing Music of Two Punjabs

There's Shae Gill in the West Punjab who embodies the Elegance, soulfulness and meaningfulness of their music.

Then there's Shehnaz Gill who embodies East Punjab's noisy, senseless and unnecessary music.
